page.title: 04THE KENNELS SANDON
page.content: The owners of the kennels breed labradors for their own pleasure.They first started in 1956. At the moment there are eight dogs. They eat fish, tripe, tinned meat,biscuit,raw cabbage and raw egg occasionally. They also have a bowl of milk at 10 o'clock. The lady feeds the dogs and the man takes them out every day for exercise for one hour. They are also let out into the field each day. The bitches are pregnant for 63 days.The puppies open their eyes at ten to fourteen days. The more contented the puppy the longer it takes to open its eyes. The bitches have their puppies indoors and then rest before they go out. There is central heating in the kennels.
